Class PortableMediaCreatorPlugin.HTMLTableRow

java.lang.Object
  de.iftm.dcm4che.router.plugin.PortableMediaCreatorPlugin.HTMLTableRow
Enclosing class:
PortableMediaCreatorPlugin
protected class PortableMediaCreatorPlugin.HTMLTableRow
extends java.lang.Object

This class implements an object containing a DOM table row element. It also has fields for the values of the attributes "id" and "title". The "title" attribute is used for soring the table rows. The "id" values is used as a distinct identification of the rows.

Construct a new object from the given parameters.

Parameters:
document - the DOM Document containing the table to which the rows belong.
columnValues - the array of strings containing the contents of the columns of the row.
idAttrValue - the value of the "id" attribute.
titleAttrValue - the value of the "title" attribute.
link - an optional link to a HTML file, which should be associated to the value of the last column. null, if no link should be associated.
